  "detailed_description": "\"Ladder Climbing\" is a game where little monsters climb up and down to avoid obstacles and find portals. Can you help them find their way home?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/26e494370660bc0f4c040d5abaa57c00.poster.avif?t=1717204973\" width=566 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/26e494370660bc0f4c040d5abaa57c00.webm?t=1717204973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/26e494370660bc0f4c040d5abaa57c00.mp4?t=1717204973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Although the little monsters look different, they are really triplets. They like to act together, but they have their own ideas, which is really a headache.<br></li><li>Can you imagine that such powerful little monsters couldn't even jump? Shh, don't mention it in front of them, they will be angry and won’t walk.<br></li><li>Watch out for those pretty cacti, they might give you a bite, oooh<br></li><li>If you are tired, don’t forget to drink more water to replenish your energy. I love you.<br></li><li>The most important thing is: don’t go to the wrong door!!!!!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/8b609fdae619e48cdd89fb682042aaf5.poster.avif?t=1717204973\" width=566 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/8b609fdae619e48cdd89fb682042aaf5.webm?t=1717204973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/8b609fdae619e48cdd89fb682042aaf5.mp4?t=1717204973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "\"Ladder Climbing\" is a game where little monsters climb up and down to avoid obstacles and find portals. Can you help them find their way home?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/26e494370660bc0f4c040d5abaa57c00.poster.avif?t=1717204973\" width=566 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/26e494370660bc0f4c040d5abaa57c00.webm?t=1717204973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/26e494370660bc0f4c040d5abaa57c00.mp4?t=1717204973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Although the little monsters look different, they are really triplets. They like to act together, but they have their own ideas, which is really a headache.<br></li><li>Can you imagine that such powerful little monsters couldn't even jump? Shh, don't mention it in front of them, they will be angry and won’t walk.<br></li><li>Watch out for those pretty cacti, they might give you a bite, oooh<br></li><li>If you are tired, don’t forget to drink more water to replenish your energy. I love you.<br></li><li>The most important thing is: don’t go to the wrong door!!!!!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/8b609fdae619e48cdd89fb682042aaf5.poster.avif?t=1717204973\" width=566 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/8b609fdae619e48cdd89fb682042aaf5.webm?t=1717204973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854700/extras/8b609fdae619e48cdd89fb682042aaf5.